actives.name: Opensea
actives.intro: OpenSea is the world's first and largest web3 marketplace for NFTs and crypto collectibles. Browse, create, buy, sell, and auction NFTs using OpenSea today.

actives.name: Blur
actives.intro: Blur is a unique non-fungible token (NFT) marketplace and aggregator platform that offers advanced features such as real-time price feeds, portfolio management and multi-marketplace NFT comparisons.

actives.name: Cryptopunks
actives.intro: CryptoPunks is a non-fungible token (NFT) collection on the Ethereum blockchain.
